summary: a castle with an imersive and intense story!
descriptionHtml: Wolfpack was founded by Kyle. Soon after led by Faloan. While Kyle and Evander are running it in the background. The story will have a deceptive twist and unique attachment of loyalty and trust to followers to come. The castle is nearing completion and npc\'s are nearly done we just have some scripting to do. Be preared for an amazing story that you will love! if you have ideas please share them, even if you just want to be in the mod let us know. :) We will try to make the updates only days apart so you have something constantly new to do.
author: Gray and Red
